Thank you for downloading ClustrixDB. To install, please navigate to the folder
containing the installation files, then run the following at the command
prompt:

./clxnode_install.py

then follow the instructions provided by the installer. More detailed
instructions can be found at
http://docs.clustrix.com/display/CLXDOC/Getting+Started+on+ClustrixDB+Software

If you run into issues or have questions please visit ClustrixDB Community
Support at https://support.clustrix.com/
